{"word":"τάχα","slug":"τάχα","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>τάχα</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><el>τᾰχύς</el>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>quickly, presently, forthwith</i>, <a href='S:Latin'>Lat.</a> <el>statim</el>, <b><a href='S:Homer'>Hom.</a></b>, etc<p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>perhaps</i>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>:—so also <el>τάχ' ἄν</el> <i>probably, perhaps, may be</i>, with <a href='S:optative mood'>opt.</a>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, attic:— <el>τάχ' ἄν</el> alone, in answers, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>:— <a href='S:strengthened'>strengthd.</a>, <el>ἴσως τάχα</el> <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>; <el>τάχα τοίνυν ἴσως</el> <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b>; <el>τάχ' ἂν ἴσως</el> <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>III. </b>for <a href='S:Comparative'>comp.</a> <el>τάχιον</el>, <a href='S:Superlative'>Sup.</a> <el>τάχιστα</el>, <a href='S:vide'>v.</a> <a href='S:ταχύς'><el>ταχύς</el></a> <a href='S:cum'>c.</a><p/></div>"}]}